  objectName: Wedding Photo
  objectSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 42f2ecb9ad51e4793a2cf9eaeadb90f2, type: 3}
  glowSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 2cc74c791f1484d1da9c860662ce5421, type: 3}
  shortDescription: A framed photo from our wedding day, 1979. Robert in his father's
    too-short tie.
  fullStory: 47 years of marriage. The day they promised forever, not knowing what
    forever would mean. Offshore account 4014 has been active since 1999.
  marthaContext: "It was always just the two of us. Bad investments. Robert was never
    careful with money \u2014 he was too proud to admit it. They never needed anything
    more than each other."
  davidContext: "Robert has been paying child support since the late 1990s. A woman
    named Sarah, from his old office. An affair. A daughter named Lily. 25 years
    of payments \u2014 not visits, not acknowledgment. Just money, and silence."
